query:
SELECT 
  i.id as inventoryId,
  i.productId,
  p.sku,
  p.description as productName,
  i.batch,
  wl.code as locationCode,
  wz.name as zoneName,
  i.quantity as totalQuantity,
  i.reservedQuantity,
  (i.quantity - i.reservedQuantity) as availableQuantity,
  i.status,
  i.createdAt,
  i.updatedAt
FROM inventory i
INNER JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
INNER JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
INNER JOIN warehouseZones wz ON wl.zoneId = wz.id
WHERE wl.code = 'H01-01-01';
